Package com.justai.zenbox.sdk

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RequestData
    The RequestData class contains the user's query and additional data for request processing.
    ResponseData
    The ResponseData class is common for every type of ZenboxService response.
    ResponseData.EmptyResponse
    The EmptyResponse class indicates that ZenboxService has returned an empty response.
    ResponseData.ErrorResponse
    The ErrorResponse class contains the data about an unsuccessful request.
    ResponseData.SuccessResponse
    The SuccessResponse class contains the response data of successfully processed request.
    Utterance
    The Utterance class contains an utterance for text-to-speech synthesise by TextToSpeech.
    ZenboxService
    The ZenboxService class contains the logic of Zenbox service and method for it's lifecycle control.
    ZenboxService.Builder
    The Builder class contains methods to build a new instance of ZenboxService.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    State
    The State enum contains possible values of ZenboxService states.
